Package: birmrssim
Title: Simulation Tools for the Beta Item Response Model with Response Styles (BIRM-RS)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dominik", "Vollbracht", , "d.vollbracht@rptu.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Dominik Vollbracht <d.vollbracht@rptu.de>
Description: Evaluates parameter recovery in the Beta Item Response Model 
    with Response Styles (BIRM-RS). Provides functions to simulate data from 
    the BIRM-RS, fit the model via Stan, and summarize parameter recovery across 
    customizable simulation conditions (e.g., sample size, number of items, 
    presence of ERS and ARS). Stan model files for four model variants (with 
    and without ERS and ARS) are included and accessible via system.file().
    An example simulation script is included and accessible via 
    system.file("examples", "sim_example.R", package = "birmrssim").
